Steps to setup and use for backend 
1- make a folder with any name 
2- go to terminal and paste this - {express myapp --view=ejs}
3-then in tyerminal do - cd myapp 
4-install nodemon - from chrome copy to terminal 
5-install mongoose from chrome
6-install mongoDB just in case aagain - ask chatgpt step by step for mac - it will taek a lil time
7-if the routes in mongodb code dosnt work , use the mongoDB compass already installed in system 
and connect to the localhost by pasting the link u use . 
8-then simply run the code 